<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">4. Your Account:</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">You agree to provide FastoFresh.com with accurate and complete information as required by registration for the FastoFresh Service ("Customer Registration Data"), including, but not limited to, your legal name, billing and delivery addresses, telephone number and promptly to notify FastoFresh.com of any change in your Customer Registration Data at FastoFresh upon registration, your username and password will allow you to access the FastoFresh Service. Your password should be kept strictly confidential to prevent unauthorized use. You agree to notify FastoFresh.com promptly of any unauthorized use of your password or your account. You will remain liable for any use of the FastoFresh Service until you notify FastoFresh.com of the unauthorized use, loss or theft.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">5. Reviews, Comments, Communications, and other Contents:</span></h2>
