<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Neither FastoFresh.com nor any of its directors, employees, agents, licensors or merchants (collectively, its "associates") shall be liable for damages of any kind, including, but not limited to, direct, indirect, incidental, punitive and consequential damages, arising from your use of, or inability to use, the FastoFresh service, FastoFresh.com, the internet or for any other claims related in any way to your relationship with FastoFresh.com.</span></p>
