<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">10. Termination:</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">FastoFresh.com may suspend or terminate your access to the FastoFresh Service at any time for any reason with or without notice to you. You may terminate your FastoFresh Service at any time for any reason by delivering notice in a manner provided in this Agreement which termination will be effective the day notice is received or such later date specified in the notice.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">11. Privacy and Security:</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Your privacy is very important to FastoFresh.com. Please click here to review a complete statement of our Privacy and Security Policy which also governs your use of FastoFresh.com and the FastoFresh Service.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">(a) Aggregated Information. FastoFresh.com may use aggregated information regarding its customers and usage of the FastoFresh Service (such as customer demographics and traffic patterns) and disclose such aggregated information to advertisers, partners and others for various purposes.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">(b) Third Party Service Providers. FastoFresh.com may employ other companies and individuals to perform certain functions such as delivering packages and analyzing data. They may have access to personal information to perform their functions.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">(c) Sale of Business. FastoFresh.com may transfer Customer Registration Data and other personal information in connection with the sale of FastoFresh.com or the sale or transfer of its business operations in your geographic area to a third-party provider of grocery ordering or delivery services who agrees to be bound by this Privacy Policy until you consent that such information will be governed by the policies and terms of such third party provider.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">(d) Enforcement of Agreement or Compliance with Law. FastoFresh.com may use or disclose personal information when FastoFresh.com believes it is appropriate to enforce this Agreement, to protect the rights, property or safety of FastoFresh.com or its users or to comply with the law.</span></p>
